data.description: Come fall in love with this spacious 4 bed, 2.5 bath functional and super flexible floor plan. The welcoming entry opens to a living / dining combo and flows nicely to the newly remodeled kitchen featuring modern two-tone cabinets, gleaming white quartz counters complete with new stainless appliances. Oversized breakfast bar overlooks the family room anchored by a corner fireplace. Large principal bedroom with en-suite bath features garden tub, separate shower & huge walk in closet. The fresh cohesive paint throughout and new laminate flooring adds to the sophisticated feel. Upstairs is surprisingly grand with a game room, flex room highlighted by French doors, 3 bedrooms and a full bath. 2'' faux wood blinds cover all the windows and crown molding frames each room. Garage has been improved with a new garage door opener and epoxy floor. Great location with close proximity to the Beltway and downtown. Tons of shopping,  restaurants and entertainment nearby, you will love living here!
